      <title>中国的不确定性给奢侈品行业的前景蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-uncertainty-clouds-outlook-luxury-sector-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当奢侈品公司公布第一季度业绩时，投资者正准备迎接奢侈品销售大幅放缓的局面，这反映出中国需求低迷，以及与去年中国大陆解除新冠限制措施提振销售时的情况相比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-uncertainty-clouds-outlook-luxury-sector-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 04:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
